<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: left;"><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on {!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Dear {!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c},</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">We hope that you enjoyed your role on NCS with The Challenge.&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">You will receive your full pay for this part of your role on {!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}, on {!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c}. This constitutes your pay for the days worked so far, minus tax and NI deductions.&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This payment covers the following parts of the programme - &nbsp;NCS: Personal Challenge, NCS: Team Challenge and NCS: Real Challenge Design (one or more will be relevant to your role).&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Payments for NCS: The Real Challenge Action will be communicated to you at a later date once you have completed them.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">If you working on a pilot, there may be some differences in pay, please contact your local staffing team if you require more information.&nbsp;</span></p><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Your full gross pay for undertaking this part of the role on this wave is {!Job_placement__c.Total_Amount_to_Pay__c}. This is subject to tax and National Insurance contributions.&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">On your payslip&nbsp;</span><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">(sent via email on&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c})</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">, you will see the total amount which you will receive.&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px;">Due to new auto-enrolment legislation, employees of The Challenge, including summer staff, will be automatically enrolled in a workplace pension scheme. This is a way of saving for your retirement that's arranged by your employer. This affects staff who earn more than Â£473 per month and are aged between 22 and state pension age. You will see your pension contributions on your payslip. For further information, please go to&nbsp;<a href="http://www.gov.uk/workplace-pensions" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">www.gov.uk/workplace-<wbr>pensions</a>.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px;"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px;">Further communications</font><span style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, including how to opt out,</span><span style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;will be sent to you in September where we will start to process all summer staff for auto-enrolment. At that point, i</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">f you would like to opt out of the pension scheme, you will need an opt-out form from The People's Pension, which you can get from and then return to by emailing&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:thepeoplespension@bandce.co.uk" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">thepeoplespension@<wbr>bandce.co.uk</a><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Staff will have a one month opt-out period: this begins from the day the administration for their becoming a member is complete, i.e. one month from the date of enrolment, which will not take place until September.</span></div><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">If you have any questions, do let us know.</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Yours sincerely,</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">NCS with The Challenge</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">4.2.1</font></p></div>]]></td>
